name: The Sands of Time
description: Taken in the Dubai Desert (part of the Arabian Desert), this photo means more to me than a pretty picture of the sandy dunes and the blazing hot sun. It reminds me of the spirit of adventure and wanderlust! It also reminds me of the time I realized how easy it was to get lost in the desert, with nothing around you but sand stretching for miles as far as the eyes can see, and a few decrepit marks of nature. The tracks made by the MPVs and our feet mean nothing, for they will soon fade away like the million of tracks left before ours.
